721
00:44:39,719 --> 00:44:41,803
Books on every subject ever studied

722
00:44:41,888 --> 00:44:44,681
by every author
who ever set pen to paper.

723
00:46:24,657 --> 00:46:28,076
-Why did you come here?
-I'm... I'm sorry.

